Texts.Chs: 把^green;组培器官^reset;带给我。(位于^orange;科学前哨站^reset;)
Texts.Eng: Bring the ^green;Tissue Culture^reset; to me at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;

Texts.Chs: 做得很好。作为感谢把这个拿去吧。这是非常少见的，你应该会用到的。
Texts.Eng: You're doing great. As a thanks, take this. It's rare, but it might come in handy some day.

Texts.Chs: ^orange;植物纤维^reset;足够萃取一小部分^green;组培器官^reset;了，不会有什么损失。带5份来给我。
Texts.Eng: ^orange;Plant Fibre^reset; is plentiful enough that extracting some for a little ^green;tissue culture^reset; won't hurt. Bring me 5.
